<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,serif; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;“Well, hello young ladies,” Mom says softly. She reaches beneath her tunic to a hand-sewn compartment in the lining. I have a small taser in mine.
