<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,serif; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">“Somerset calls me Monkey,” says the child. “’Cos I can hold on tight.”</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%">
