<span style="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,serif; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">“A lucky guess. Got a question for you. How does a bloody Temprat learn to talk like that? Aren’t you all bred from birth to roll holy?”</span></p>
