<span style="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,serif; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">When I arrive at Taft’s office he’s not there. I sit down at his desk, and toy with the idea of trying to access his Hydra. Before I can decide if
