<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,serif; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">“I take it you’re not volunteering for the job,” says Wilder.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,serif; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">“I might, if I wanted to risk spawning your unholy devil child,” snarls Taft.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,serif; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">“Big talker,” says Wilder.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,serif; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">“It might be worth it. Just to see if you actually bend anywhere. Alas, my heart belongs to another.”</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,serif; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">“To say they have my sympathy doesn’t begin to cover it,” says Wilder</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,serif; mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Okay. Not what I expected from these two. Not even remotely. I’m waiting for more sparkling repartee, but I hear Nan’s heels click across the floor
